months has been on the battlefield the iraqis have recaptured a 
series of border areas to gain an edge in the conflict with iran 
baghdad radio quoting a military communique reported that 
iraqi warplanes hit two large maritime targets which usually 
means tankers off the iranian coast at 10 pm friday 3 pm edt 
