<TEXT>
when doug la follette tossed his hat in the 
ring for the us senate some people wondered why the hat was so 
big 
la follette wisconsins secretary of state wears a gray 
australian bush hat almost everywhere he goes the reason is he 
has the same mild form of skin cancer as president reagan 
his widebrimmed hat is a slight political liability but also a 
potential trademark and a tool for educating people about the 
hazards of excessive exposure to the sun la follette said 
i dont wear a hat out of a quirk i wear a hat for very 
realistic health reasons la follette 48 said during a campaign 
visit at a recent farmers market on capitol square ive learned 
that the sun can be harmful 
la follette is one of five democrats and two republicans vying 
to succeed retiring sen william proxmire dwis 
its very sobering realizing being brown is not as beautiful 
as you think it is said la follette who was diagnosed three 
years ago as having basal cell carcinoma the most common and least 
dangerous form of skin cancer 
nationally an estimated 300000 to 400000 people are diagnosed 
each year as having the easily treated form of cancer it is not 
even counted in official cancer statistics but still could be 
fatal if untreated 
la follettes case was diagnosed when what he thought was a 
pimple turned out to be a precancerous spot on his skin since 
then he has gone in for a checkup every six months 
his physician dr stephen snow of the university of wisconsin 
medical school said skin cancer accounts for more than onethird 
of all cancer cases and as many skin cancers are diagnosed 
annually as cancers of the lung breast colon and prostate 
combined 
its all related to sunlight snow said its a totally 
preventable problem but since when has the average person ever 
been rational 
dr derek cripps also of the university of wisconsin 
recommends that everyone wear sun screen with a protection factor 
of 15 or higher la follette wears sun screen rated 32 as well as 
his widebrimmed hat 
wearing a hat puts off some people la follette said 
you cant be a hermit the hat is my solution la follette 
said the big brim is important because it keeps the sun off my 
nose and ears 
</TEXT>
